Just floor 2 is not big enough for that many people but otherwise nice people the classes are quite good but sometimes "boring" without being nasty. Little advice: don't force people to learn lessons, let them learn it yourself, it will give them more space to express themselves. I see that it was after we moved to the Danielle group that we really relaxed, but the classes before it were quite boring, I hope you could improve, it's a small point for people who need (I speak for the little ones aged 14 to 7 because I think they are suffocating and they don't dare say it tell the stories with joy make jokes with the student when they all smile that's where you would have understood that he need to change give them more space And may God put you on the right path.
